Hey guys, just a quick one on dates. I want to display something different depending on season. If today is winter (November-January), display X. What's my best option?

```{% set month = today|datetimeformat( '%m' ) %}
{% if month is 11 %}
(% set season == "Winter" %}
&lt;!-- repeat for month 12 and 1 --&gt;
&lt;!-- repeat for other months and seasons, close if--&gt;

{% if season == "Winter" %}
Winter sale!
{% elif season == "Spring" %}
Spring sale
&lt;!--etc...--&gt;```
